{"tid":1556022,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【大學】任嘉兒　宣佈復出！！！","createTime":"2019-09-09T14:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T02:14:10.000Z","uid":133064,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4e8cea47cc3abd2507eacee59f3cf4ec4d0baf5f","tid":1556022,"uid":133064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:39:35.000Z","msg":"【繼續並肩作戰吧！】<br />\n<br />\n我的心願從來都很簡單，無論是辭去工作，抑或早前決定退出，都是本著兄弟爬山的精神，望能成功光復議會。<br />\n<br />\n功成從來不必有我。當初願意主動讓路，最大原因，只是不想重蹈以往「鷸蚌相爭，漁人得利」的覆轍。<br />\n<br />\n自宣佈退出之後，我一直收到很多很多支持和鼓勵，衷心感謝大家的厚愛！<br />\n<br />\n我宣布撤回退出決定，繼續與大家同行！<br />\n<br />\n往後的日子，一起並肩作戰吧﹗<br />\n<br />\n------------------<br />\n<br />\n支持任嘉兒妹妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a9254bc50f5ba192adfe8b87f6a3830a6af56b","tid":1556022,"uid":133064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:40:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/camilleyamkayi/posts/1396757347130157\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcamilleyamkayi%2Fposts%2F1396757347130157&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNpUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=6238454d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/camilleyamkayi/posts/1396757347130157</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095e6eb1db262adf032071ecfcbef84f2eb13731","tid":1556022,"uid":133064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:41:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c54b18c066493f401b70df6ebe4cbf0fd788d8","tid":1556022,"uid":133064,